version_description:
We’ve made it easier than ever to order and pay for your Corner Bakery favorites! Go from craving our made-to-order breakfast, lunch and dinner items to enjoying the satisfying flavors even faster. Plus, save time by ordering in app and skipping the line when you pick up in cafe.

FEATURES:
· Pay in the app and skip the line when picking up your order.
· Browse our menu, place an order, and find locations near you.
· Save your favorite orders and location for easy reordering.

If you would like to give us feedback or have any issues, please use the Contact Us button in the app. By clicking on “App Support” you can reach out to our technical support team or “Corner Bakery Support” for any other potential issues or feedback.
